### Images tags format explained at https://github.com/wodby/docker4drupal#images-tags

### PROJECT SETTINGS

PROJECT_NAME=my_drupal11_project
PROJECT_BASE_URL=drupal.docker.localhost
PROJECT_PORT=8000

DB_NAME=drupal
DB_USER=drupal
DB_PASSWORD=drupal
DB_ROOT_PASSWORD=password
DB_HOST=mariadb
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DRIVER=mysql

